  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast is served buffet-style, with a range of hot and cold options on offer.</p>
<p>The half board includes a four-course evening meal, chosen from the à la carte menu. Expect classic Swiss dishes with a Mediterranean twist.</p>
<p>When weather permits, you can enjoy both breakfast and dinner on the lovely lakefront terrace.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
