  <description><![CDATA[<p>The historic Romantik Hotel Beau Rivage is in the quiet lakeside town of Weggis. It's an easy stroll from the picturesque harbour where you can jump on a ferry to explore the lake or head to the elegant city of Lucerne. A ten-minute walk will get you to the lift up Mount Rigi where there's countless walks and spectacular views in all directions.</p>
<h2>Exceptional service &amp; lakeside dining</h2>
<p>The friendly team provide exceptional service - settle in and enjoy the leisurely pace of life by the lake. Meals are a delicious mix of French and international cuisine that can be enjoyed on the lakeside terrace.</p>
<h2>Relax in the garden and spa</h2>
<p>Laze in the garden and bask in the sun on the comfortable poolside loungers. Immerse yourself in nature with swims in the lake - there's a private access point to the lake immediately in front of the hotel. For a touch more relaxation head to the spa, which has a sauna, steam room, and a crystal-salt whirlpool.</p>]]></description>
