  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Beau Rivage is the only four-star hotel in central Weggis that sits directly on the lake, and the ferry port and the Rigi cable car are both within easy walking distance. Enjoy beautiful gardens, an outdoor pool, and direct access to the lake. Top your day off with fine French cuisine and drinks on the lakeside terrace.</p>]]></listingDescription>
